{"tid":1537064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去美國領事館之前同我簽咗呢個白宮聯署佢","createTime":"2019-09-03T19:48:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T05:28:39.000Z","uid":193565,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"99906fe6a1b3c485f63a94871de06537749dbe75","tid":1537064,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:48:54.000Z","msg":"之前已經有聯署話要制裁狗官，但而家<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警都一定要清算埋</span>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-police-violating-basic-human-rights\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-police-violating-basic-human-rights&d=8FXSm2SwW1drj%2BZzPONh3ItKjO%2FIGoH7AJS0Ocrd4mI%3D&h=91172122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-police-violating-basic-human-rights</a><br />\n<br />\n人手翻譯<br />\n《以違反基本人權為由制裁所有香港警察》<br />\n鑑於香港警察於執法時違反人權，我們敦促美國政府透過全球馬格尼茨基人權問責法制裁所有香港警察，相關事件包括但不限於：<br />\n<br />\n非人化：稱示威者為蟑螂<br />\n酷刑：於醫院中性侵害、暴力對待被捕且無反抗能力之市民，於沙田、旺角屈斷已被制服人士之手腕<br />\n侮辱：於黃大仙搜身時要求市民下跪<br />\n暴力：於9月3日將一名市民毆打至失去意識並阻礙救援工作<br />\n毒害：於民居附近、地鐵站施放催淚彈，並懷疑使用過期催淚彈<br />\n懷疑警黑合作：縱容黑社會人士於元朗站施襲<br />\n<br />\n800字母上限已經用盡，但黑警暴行仍未能盡錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">用崑崙銀行啦屌你老母</span></span>"},{"pid":"1142ada2140094fa8112c446793995a8ce1f4776","tid":1537064,"uid":297850,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:49:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MM8t4q5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMM8t4q5.jpg&h=4e6f0be1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f20a8983dcdd973d4a859c4b80ee8199063150b7","tid":1537064,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:49:50.000Z","msg":"1<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g