n(3) 不平等條約無效論是謊言<br />\n(4) 中華民國早已放棄香港的主權<br />\n(5) 中華人民共和國以武力脅迫大英國移交香港主權不合國際法<br />\n(6) 70年代聯合國從非自治領名單剔除香港<br />\n(7) 中英聯合聲明違反住民自決原則<br />\n(8) 香港符合《蒙特維多國家權利及義務公約》中「國家」的定義<br />\n(9) 香港軍事史<br />\n<br />\n請幫推以下post！<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><ins><span style=\"color: violet;\">香港人一定要知！</span></ins></strong></span></span>一定一定要睇！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">香港史實在此！勿做港豬！想贏就入嚟！</span></span></span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d87b9faf1dac007978d33fd4b114cc90aa0efd4c","tid":1537064,"uid":287757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:14:56.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1be5cbc3054393ffa83d8fbb63a3470778339639","tid":1537064,"uid":299171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T20:37:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文敘述歡迎改動</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nHong Kong police ordered immediate closure of Prince Edward metro station and dispersed reporters and paramedics after attacking passengers indiscriminately on 31 Aug. Three seriously wounded passengers have gone missing since the same day.<br />\n<br />\nThe metro station reopened on 2 Sep. Requests to disclose CCTV footage were denied. The three missing passengers have not yet been found.<br />\n<br />\nThree fatal cases were revealed within the same day on 3 Sep."},{"pid":"e580a38f6ab93680e4383a65fcdc10579b810590","tid":1537064,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"99906fe6a1b3c485f63a94871de06537749dbe75","tid":1537064,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T19:48:54.000Z","msg":"之前已經有聯署話要制裁狗官，但而家<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警都一定要清算埋</span>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.go